On Screen Display for Raspberry Pi and various sensors.

This project aim using a Raspberry pi for On screen Display, in FPV context for controling a RC plane model.

This project was made by Christian Muller for his internship during his Master degree on the he-arc ingenering school, under David Grunenwald supervision and Cyrille Henry mandate.

demonstration video:
http://vimeo.com/98249321

 QtOSD : OSD using Qt and QML
 demo : main software
 recorder : get sensors and video data
